vice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"frontend->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"EmailService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"EmailService异常平均耗时8265949ms，比正常耗时20201ms高出409倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService异常平均耗时8297239ms，比正常耗时154368ms高出53倍。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n通过上述数据可以看出，**EmailService** 在异常时间段内是主要的性能瓶颈，严重影响了系统的响应时间。进一步的分析可集中在 EmailService 的资源使用和网络问题以确认根因。"}
